{"tid":876442,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[8日7夜] [多圖多字] 札榥小樽深度遊","createTime":"2018-10-25T15:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T16:49:04.000Z","uid":73311,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8fc4a2ce51d43b1d0b4be49d376694e1e914e8","tid":876442,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"小弟第二次寫遊記, 寫得唔好請屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個旅行係舊年11月既事, 突然有衝動想記錄同分享下 <br />\n<br />\n呢次係我第一次去北海道, 因為就到年尾<br />\nd大假如果唔放左佢就會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我緊係拿拿林請假去旅行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同朋友黎個快閃之旅都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好多行程都無時間plan,  純粹係當放鬆心情之旅~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.s 決定早朋友兩日去, 自己鳩行下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇過, 好似得Cx/HK Airline/ANA 先有直航去北海道<br />\n咁另外兩家航空都貴好多, 所以選擇左HK Airline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n機票包20kg來回+保險+稅大約HKD$3900<br />\n住方面我Book左2間 : <br />\n2晚札榥Hostel自己住+5晚札榥Airbnb同朋友住<br />\n加埋大約HKD 1000樓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講返個行程啦, 因為太趕住出發.....<br />\n事前係無時間認真計劃每日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>8日7夜都會留返係札榥小樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n所以好多景點雖然想睇, 但都無打算去<br />\n只係略略計劃下個方向就出發<br />\n去之前都預左只係會行下街, 食下野, 買下野等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個Trip(機票+住宿+食野+搭車+買手信) 大約用左HKD 10000 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>原諒我會係呢個遊記有好多廢噏, 因為我真係好鐘意分享!</strong><br />\n<strong>(唔鐘意聽廢噏可以上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</strong><br />\n<br />\n我全程係用Iphone影相, 我唔識構圖同執相<br />\n所以有好多相都斜斜地, 影得唔好, 請見諒 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw我都知我有d朋友都有上開連登<br />\n唔該唔好同我相認Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好, 出發!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Day 1 香港-&gt;新千歲機場-&gt;札榥住宿</strong><br />\n<br />\n朝早07:55機-&gt;關西機場14:55 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hywKkLB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhywKkLB.jpg&h=08f96f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港人必影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於到左新千歲機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xastNq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxastNq3.jpg&h=2e2bdc1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cxts2Zr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxts2Zr.jpg&h=ad124862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoaK5cN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoaK5cN.jpg&h=9ae0738e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBkfsq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBkfsq9.jpg&h=fa299940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TripkMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTripkMa.jpg&h=e0f38609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約日本時間1點幾就黎2點,比原定時間好似早左一個鐘到, Lucky!<br />\n<br />\n新千歲機場都幾多野睇<br />\n但因為Plan左最後一日先黎機場睇野<br />\n所以略略行過下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一出門口已經感覺到個陣涼意<br />\n黎之前已經Check左天氣<br />\n都係2-10度左右, 天氣唔會有大太陽, 陰陰地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁一出機場就走去買JR車票出市區間Hostel Check In啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zysJBkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzysJBkd.jpg&h=276cdfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能因為天氣問題啦&hellip;我覺得好荒蕪, 灰灰暗暗咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZctNsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZctNsa.jpg&h=e75a8bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北海道, 同想像中好似有小小出入&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但到站後, 出左JR就好返小小, 終於見返d人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LegN20Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLegN20Q.jpg&h=2e616da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我今次頭2晚會住距離札榥JR站5-10分鐘路程既Hostel<br />\n叫Ten To Ten Hostel, 間野真係好近,又幾易搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上一出札榥 JR 西出口,直行到底再過馬路轉入去小路就係啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pkvgms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pkvgms.jpg&h=4fc17861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFuDqeP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFuDqeP.jpg&h=8a31def1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVe721w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVe721w.jpg&h=af7a69b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JigVstd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJigVstd.jpg&h=6707d9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6v9sizU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6v9sizU.jpg&h=a742bbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KHp5eV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KHp5eV.jpg&h=67063a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tye4kOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTye4kOi.jpg&h=99b22d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間Hostel大約係咁, 我住10人Dorm<br />\n房既空間感覺唔大, 但我個人覺得床既空間其實都幾大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z61BWn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz61BWn0.jpg&h=8176a1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VK4kPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VK4kPG.jpg&h=17268208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDSJBn2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDSJBn2.jpg&h=8adc8a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLfry9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLfry9J.jpg&h=a9191add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至少夠放哂我個袋,仲唔會覺得逼, 而且仲有一個細燈<br />\n一開頭睇相幾驚無簾, 不過好在係有既,咁都有D私人空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外間房有locker,有一個細雪櫃可以放飲品<br />\n不過唔可以係房食野飲野<br />\n要到樓下一樓個圖書館Share area食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRbBWoN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRbBWoN.jpg&h=ff932c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck in既時候佢會送兩張2張coupon<br />\nwelcome drink同cafe早餐coupon<br />\nOrder 500yen就有減300yen<br />\n(咁我2張野都有用哂, 唔好浪費呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AU7p5hb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAU7p5hb.jpg&h=f8916643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就出發去搵食啦!<br />\n好撚肚餓呀屌!, 幾乎係全日無食過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係機場飲左杯咖啡就上機<br />\nHK Airline個飛機餐難食到食左一啖停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n離開Hostel大約係晏就3點半左右, 個天仲光光猛猛<br />\n<br />\n因為想食拉麵, 於是問左Hostel個姐姐附近有咩好食既拉麵<br />\n佢話可以行去薄野個邊, 有條小巷叫元祖札幌拉麵橫丁<br />\n咁我本身都無搵過有邊間想食, 所以決定去到個邊再算!<br />\n<br />\n一路Keep住向右行, 都要行成半粒鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceJD9LA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceJD9LA.jpg&h=436cd909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8gVsxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8gVsxh.jpg&h=047ffc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQzTeci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQzTeci.jpg&h=c30af9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPkvgqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPkvgqE.jpg&h=adfca0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSnhFSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSnhFSk.jpg&h=2574bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zX9cuLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzX9cuLG.jpg&h=7547b08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZy45jT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZy45jT.jpg&h=e998b0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下見到呢個建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bH5vgq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbH5vgq9.jpg&h=0bffe4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知咩名堂,我記得係網上咩十大札榥必去景點之一<br />\n但因為個天已經好黑,同埋可能已經關門, 所以就無入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDMeH6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDMeH6E.jpg&h=e0bd76ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係條巷行左幾次來回都決定唔到食邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後是但入一間食, 叫咩倍煎舍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aH16zef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaH16zef.jpg&h=0daa1bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKGN26N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKGN26N.jpg&h=31c6f19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都幾好食, 係咸左d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完之後行返同一條路返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Uq3BsJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Uq3BsJ.jpg&h=f7542996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jTdeep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jTdeep.jpg&h=98de5292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個燈塔,再影下相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQNxuNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQNxuNt.jpg&h=a74a8465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0reH7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0reH7u.jpg&h=0dc9096f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實夜晚都幾撚凍, 好在有帶頸巾<br />\n我覺得係救左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時間仲早<br />\n入左札榥 JR附近既商場行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完個拉麵硬係覺得唔夠飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以入左Mister Donut, 啪左兩個Donut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TDQgs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TDQgs4.jpg&h=75c58048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完真係覺得好撚肥好撚飽, 好罪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHostel附近有間Yodabashi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iPDqoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iPDqoG.jpg&h=8d41f487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以走左去人地舖頭按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n按左成粒鐘都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UhKPw3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUhKPw3X.jpg&h=1e435c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EcEgb3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcEgb3Z.jpg&h=f4fa1fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOn5PQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOn5PQF.jpg&h=13b2e22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你老味, 舉到我隻腳咁撚高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vS973aG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvS973aG.jpg&h=900622b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uw1iqo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuw1iqo2.jpg&h=05593529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n厚顏無恥按到人地收舖先肯走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實之前都試過自己黎日本旅行<br />\n仲記得第一次既感覺係好sad好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過今次既感覺唔強烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完! 沖涼訓教! <br />\n結束今日既行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b581aa36b2d0b905ca9eb9f2f3c2a0097bb71d73","tid":876442,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"開錯台, 重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[8日7夜] [多圖多字] 札榥小樽深度遊~<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bJnirT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bJnirT</a>"}]}